WEBVTT

00:12:29.185 --> 00:12:31.937
Internet affords us now.

00:12:31.937 --> 00:12:36.324
But a real challenge is to find, to design

00:12:36.324 --> 00:12:39.753
to create, to empower those connectors

00:12:39.753 --> 00:12:43.572
that are able to innovate, to transform

00:12:43.572 --> 00:12:46.240
noise and silence into signal

00:12:46.240 --> 00:12:48.178
and finally bring our democracies

00:12:48.178 --> 00:12:50.506
to the 21st century.

00:12:50.506 --> 00:12:53.237
I'm not saying it's easy.

00:12:53.237 --> 00:12:56.820
But in our experience, we actually stand a chance

00:12:56.820 --> 00:12:59.154
of making it work.

00:12:59.154 --> 00:13:02.286
And in my heart, it's most definitely